<b class="paperTitle"><a href="papers/CISS17.pdf" target="_blank">Fundamental Limits of Location Privacy Using Anonymization</a></b> <br>
<span class="paperAuthor">&nbsp;  <a href="">Nazanin Takbiri</a>, <b>Amir Houmansadr</b>, <a href="http://www-unix.ecs.umass.edu/~dgoeckel/" target="_blank">Dennis Goeckel</a>, and <a href="http://www.ecs.umass.edu/ece/pishro/" target="_blank">Hossein Pishro-Nik</a><br>
