<b class="paperTitle"><a href="papers/CovertCast-PETS16.pdf" target="_blank">CovertCast: Using Live Streaming to Evade Internet Censorship</a></b> <br>
<span class="paperAuthor">&nbsp;  <a href="http://www.cs.utexas.edu/~richard/"  target="_blank">Richard McPherson</a>, <b>Amir Houmansadr</b>, and <a href="http://www.cs.cornell.edu/~shmat/" target="_blank">Vitaly Shmatikov</a><br>
