<b class="paperTitle"><a href="papers/IH11-Stegobot.pdf" >Stegobot: A Covert Social Network Botnet</a></b> <br>
<span class="paperAuthor">&nbsp; <a href="http://www.hatswitch.org/~sn275">Shishir Nagaraja</a>, <b>Amir Houmansadr</b>, Pragya Agarwal, Vijit Kumar, Pratch Piyawongwisal, and <a href="http://hatswitch.org/~nikita/">Nikita Borisov</a><br>
